nterface to easily\n    implement numerical methods.\n  license: BSD-3-Clause\n  license_file: LICENSE\n  homepage: https://github.com/hpc-maths/samurai\n  documentation: https://hpc-math-samurai.readthedocs.io\n\nextra:\n  recipe-maintainers:\n    - gouarin\n    - pmatalon\n",
